text: Castets-en-Dorthe was a commune. It was in the region Nouvelle-Aquitaine in the Gironde department in southwest France. On 1 January 2017, it was became part of the new commune, Castets et Castillon.Arrêté préfectoral 1 August 2016 == References == Category:Former communes in Gironde
title: Castets-en-Dorthe
